name: Moore AI
description: More-AI is also called intelligent arbitrage robot. The robot will identify and capture the price difference and trading volume of digital assets on various trading platforms by itself, decide whether to carry out arbitrage task, and start arbitrage trading by itself at the appropriate time: Including hedge arbitrage and gambling arbitrage trading, the assets entrusted by us can be completely unaffected by the rise and fall of prices, which solves all kinds of disadvantages and risks of artificial arbitrage.
